info.description: Cooperative game where players move around board to eliminate diseases. Players win by curing all four diseases and lose if diseases spread too far or cures take too long.
info.helpText: Players choose seats. Select options using gear icon. Press restart icon to begin (and to automatically set up board if that option is chosen). After play begins, all disease markers are moved by players. To automatically move disease markers of that city color, click on that city holder. To return disease marker to holder, click on marker. Cities only hold 3 markers; manually place other markers nearby. To change outbreak counter, just click on it. If a card needs to be removed from the board, drag it to the trash can holder in the bottom right.

Dispatch.power:
- Move any player to city with another player
- Move another player as if it were you, using your cards

Medical.power:
- Remove all disease markers of same color when treat disease
- Remove markers of cured disease from city currently in

Operations.power:
- Build research station in city currently in without card
- Move from research station to any city with any city card

Plans.power: - Take any discarded event card to reuse one time later (card is not part of player's hand)

Research.power: - Give or receive any city card when share knowledge

Science.power: - Use only 4 cards when discover cure

Specialist.power: - Prevent disease marker from being placed in city currently in and all connected cities

fields.text: You are about to start a new game.  Are you sure?

eventDetail.text:
1. Quiet: Skip next infect cities step and do not flip over cards.
2. Airlift: Move any 1 pawn to any city.
3. Forecast: Draw, look at, rearrange, and return top 6 infection cards.
4. Resilient: Remove any 1 card from infection discard pile from game.
5. Grant: Add 1 research station to any 1 city without using a city card.

eventDetail1.text:
1. Do 4 actions
  a) Move
     - To a city connected with a line
     - To city named on card which you discard
     - To any city if you discard city card you are currently in
     - From city with research station to another city with research station
  b) Build
     - Discard card matching city currently in to build research station
  c) Treat
     - Remove 1 disease marker from city currently in (all markers if cured)
  d) Share
     - Give or take card matching city currently in with another player in same city
  e) Cure
     - In city with research station, discard 5 city cards of same color
2. Draw 2 player cards
3. Infect cities

fields.text: Do you want to remove this object from the board?

epidemicDetail.text:
1. Increase.
   - Advance infection marker 1 space.
2. Infect.
   - Press 'Deal Bottom Card Button.' Add three markers to that city (or start outbreak if city already has any cubes of that color).
3. Intensify.
   - Press 'Shuffle and Return' button.
